text: Jens Fredricson (born 14 December 1967) is a Swedish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
